oks/review/new-crime-novels.html</link><description>我们的专栏作家介绍本月最佳新版本。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/13/books/review/new-crime-novels.html</guid></item><item><title>用这些引起争议的书来测试一下自己</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/01/13/books/review/controversial-books-quiz.html</link><description>尝试一下这个关于 20 世纪上半叶文学的小测验，这些文学曾引起审查制度的挑战——而且现在仍然如此。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 15:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/01/13/books/review/controversial-books-quiz.html</guid></item><item><title>书评：《我亲爱的男孩》，作者：约翰·杜弗雷</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/13/books/review/my-darling-boy-john-dufresne.html</link><description>在约翰·杜弗雷尼的新书《我亲爱的男孩》中，一位退休记者奋力将他的儿子从阿片类药物的痛苦中解救出来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/13/books/review/my-darling-boy-john-dufresne.html</guid></item><item><title>理查德·海斯，76 岁，去世；心意发生惊人转变的神学家</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/12/us/richard-hays-dead.html</link><description>他断言对圣经的深入阅读表明同性关系不是有罪的，这对福音派世界发出了一声雷鸣。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 21:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/12/us/richard-hays-dead.html</guid></item><item><title>写作幻想是自然而然的。现实要令人畏惧得多。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/12/books/nnedi-okorafor-death-of-author.html</link><description>在赢得几乎所有主要科幻小说和奇幻小说奖项后，尼迪·奥科拉福在她迄今为止最具自传性的小说中探索了她自己历史上的创伤事件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/12/books/nnedi-okorafor-death-of-author.html</guid></item></channel></rss>